Content.bodyText:
Hey Darren,

Thanks for the feedback - really appreciate it.

FYI, FOWD is not multi-track. It's 1-track like FOWA Dublin. I'm sorry you got that impression. Can you please let me know how you got that impression? Maybe our site doesn't make it clear.

Best,
Ryan
